  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Although the name suggests a ranged weapon, a stun gun requires physical contact to affect its target. The Taser is a ranged weapon with a similar effect. On a successful hit, the stun gun deals 1d3 Electricity damage (do not add the character&rsquo;s POW bonus), and the target must make a Fortitude Saving Throw [TN15] or be paralyzed for 1d6 rounds. Improvised versions of this weapon include cattle prods and electric cords with stripped insulation.</p>",
